{"id": "aos006", "name": "Audio_Academy_694_08_12", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "The heck... Where did she go?\nAh, Thomas; have you seen Aroma? I need to give her the lecture materials from last semester. \n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate A"], "content": "Hmm, I don't think I have.\nI think she stayed in the music classroom after our previous music lesson ended. Maybe you can take a look there?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Got it. Thanks!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_5", "Music"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Woah! You scared me...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Ah, sorry~ But your singing is amazing... It's been a while since I last heard you sing.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Here, these are for you. Some extra materials from last semester as well as the visual aids for the lectures.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Ah, but I guess you probably don't need them... You were supposed to be behind by almost a year, yet after you came back, your grades caught up with Daniel and me in like an instant.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "That's not a big deal...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "By the way, what song was that?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... I don't know myself either. I just got this nostalgic feeling, and the words just sort of came out by themselves...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Hoho, so you still remember quite a few things. Then I'm sure that your memory will also recover in no time as well!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Yes...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "On a side note... I didn't know that Aroma knows how to play the piano?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "...... Eh? I, I don't know...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "I've never heard you play it before. That's awesome!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aw, come on... Don't put on a long face all the time. I was serious when I said you were awesome. Your grades are good; your singing voice is beautiful; you are talented in other things too... Most importantly, you look so adorable and you have this flawless~ skin~ Seriously, did you type in some cheat code for life? You have to remember what an amazing person you are~ Take this take this~\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Ahahah... Stop it, that tickles...\nThank you... But...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Hmm? What's the matter?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "I don't know... I just feel like the people in class don't really like me... \nBefore my accident... did something happen?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Ah~ That's... I say you should just ignore those people! I'm 99.99% sure that they are just jealous of you because you are simply too perfect! No need to worry!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "I see...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Let's go! Iris is waiting for us. We should eat lunch together!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Sure.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "もう……どこ行っちゃったの？\nあ、Thomas！Aroma見なかった？\n前学期の資料渡そうと思ってたんだけど……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト A"], "content": "見てないけど。\nそういえば、音楽の授業の後音楽室に残ってるのを見たかな。\n行ってみれば？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "ありがとう！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_5", "音楽"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "きゃあ！ビックリした……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "あ、ごめんごめん！\nAromaの歌聴くの久しぶり……やっぱり上手だね。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "はい、これ。前学期の補足資料と講義のプレゼン。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "あー、でもAromaには必要ないかな？\n1年近くのブランクがあるのに、もう私とDanielに追いつきそうだもんね。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "そんなことないよ……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "何の歌を歌ってたの？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……分からない。\n急に懐かしくなって……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "へぇ！なんだ、結構覚えてるんじゃない！\n絶対すぐに全部思い出せるよ！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "でも……Aromaって前からピアノ弾けたっけ？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……え？分からない……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "ピアノ弾いてるところなんてはじめて見た！\nすごいね！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "もう……そんな顔しないで。\nAromaは本当にすごいよ。\n成績も良くて、歌声もきれいで、才能に溢れてる……\nそれに何より可愛いし！肌もきれいだよね～ずるいよ！\n自分がどれだけすごい人間なのか早く思い出しなさいよね～コチョコチョコチョ～\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "あはは……もう！くすぐったい……！\nありがとう……でも……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "ん？どうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "分からない……でも、クラスの人たちは私のことがあまり好きじゃないように感じるの……\n前に……なにかあったのかな？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "あ～それね……気にしないでいいよ！あんなやつら！\nAromaがあまりにも完璧だから、嫉妬してるだけ！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "行こ！Irisが待ってるよ。\n一緒にご飯食べよ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "真是的……跑到哪裡去了？\n啊，Thomas，有看到 Aroma 嗎？我要拿上學期的資料給她。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "沒耶。對了，上一堂音樂課結束後她好像待在音樂教室喔，要不要去看看？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "好，謝謝！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_5", "音樂"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哇！嚇我一跳……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊，對不起對不起～好好聽喔……好久沒聽到妳唱歌了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "來，給妳，上學期的一些補充資料還有講座的簡報。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "好，謝謝妳。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊，不過妳應該不需要吧……明明進度落後了快一年，一回來成績馬上又追上我跟 Daniel 了。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "沒有啦……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "對了，剛剛那是什麼歌啊？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……我也不知道，突然覺得很懷念就唱了……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "喔喔，還是記得很多東西的嘛，妳的記憶一定也很快就能恢復的！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "說起來……Aroma 原來會彈鋼琴的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……咦？我不知道……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "從來沒聽妳彈過耶，好厲害！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "真是的……別一直愁眉苦臉的嘛。妳真的很厲害耶，成績又好，歌聲也美，還那麼多才多藝……重點是還長得那麼可愛，皮膚也那麼好，太犯規了！快點想起來自己是多棒的人啊～我搔我搔～\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "啊哈哈……討厭，好癢啦……\n謝謝妳……不過……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "嗯？怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不知道……總覺得班上的人不是很喜歡我……\n以前……有發生過什麼事嗎？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊啊～那個啊……別管那些人啦！因為妳真的太完美了，她們只是忌妒妳而已，沒事的！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "走吧！Iris 在等我們吃午餐呢，一起過去吧。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯，好。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "정말……어디로 가버린 거지?\n앗, Thomas! 혹시 Aroma 봤니? 저번 학기 자료 좀 건네주려 하는데.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생A"], "content": "못 봤는데? 아, 전교시 음악 수업 끝나고 계속 음악실에 있는 것 같던데. 거기 가서 찾아봐.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "그렇구나! 고마워!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_5", "음악"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "으앗! 놀래라...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "아, 미안 미안~ 노래가 너무 좋아서... 네가 부르는 노래 듣는 거,  정말 오랜만이다.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "고마워.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "자, 이거. 저번 학기 보충 자료랑 강의 내용이야.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "그렇구나. 고마워.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "하하, 사실 너한테는 필요 없으려나.... 진도가 1년이나 뒤처졌다 해도, 분명 눈 깜빡할 사이에 나랑 Daniel을 따라잡을 텐데.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "그 정도는 아니야……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "참, 방금 부른 그 노래, 무슨 곡이야?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……나도 모르겠어.... 그냥 갑자기 부르고 싶어져서...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "오오~ 그래도 기억이 아직 많이 남아있는 것 같아 다행이다! 분명  머지않아 네 기억들도 전부 돌아올 거야!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응....\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "그런데……Aroma, 너 원래 피아노 칠 줄 알았니?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……어라? 나도 잘 모르겠어......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "피아노 연주하는 건 한 번도 못 들어 봤거든! 진짜 대단해!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……고마워.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "에휴 정말…… 자꾸 그런 표정 짓지 마! 넌 정말 대단한 사람이라니깐. 성적도 좋지, 노래도 잘하지, 악기도 잘 다루고 다재다능하지.... 게다가 얼굴도 귀엽고 피부까지 좋다니! 이건 반칙이야! 그러니깐 빨리 네가 얼마나 대단한 사람인지를 기억해 내야만 해! 알았지? 우쭈쭈쭈쭈!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "하하하하하…그만해, 간지럽단 말이야……\n고마워……하지만……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "응? 왜 그래?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "잘 모르겠지만……그냥 느낌에 반 애들이 나를 싫어하는 것 같아서.... 혹시 예전에... 무슨 일 있었어?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "아아～그 일은…… 그, 그런 애들은 신경 쓰지도, 관심주지도 마! 네가 너무 완벽하니깐 걔네들도 질투 나서 그러는 것뿐이니깐! 아무 일도 아니야!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응.....\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "가자! Iris가 기다리고 있어. 가서 같이 점심이나 먹자.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응, 알았어.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "真是的……跑到哪裡去了？\n啊，Thomas，有看到 Aroma 嗎？我要拿上學期的資料給她。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "沒耶。對了，上一堂音樂課結束後她好像待在音樂教室喔，要不要去看看？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "好，謝謝！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_5", "音樂"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哇！嚇我一跳……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊，對不起對不起～好好聽喔……好久沒聽到妳唱歌了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "來，給妳，上學期的一些補充資料還有講座的簡報。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "好，謝謝妳。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊，不過妳應該不需要吧……明明進度落後了快一年，一回來成績馬上又追上我跟 Daniel 了。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "沒有啦……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "對了，剛剛那是什麼歌啊？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……我也不知道，突然覺得很懷念就唱了……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "喔喔，還是記得很多東西的嘛，妳的記憶一定也很快就能恢復的！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "說起來……Aroma 原來會彈鋼琴的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……咦？我不知道……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "從來沒聽妳彈過耶，好厲害！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "真是的……別一直愁眉苦臉的嘛。妳真的很厲害耶，成績又好，歌聲也美，還那麼多才多藝……重點是還長得那麼可愛，皮膚也那麼好，太犯規了！快點想起來自己是多棒的人啊～我搔我搔～\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "啊哈哈……討厭，好癢啦……\n謝謝妳……不過……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "嗯？怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不知道……總覺得班上的人不是很喜歡我……\n以前……有發生過什麼事嗎？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊啊～那個啊……別管那些人啦！因為妳真的太完美了，她們只是忌妒妳而已，沒事的！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "走吧！Iris 在等我們吃午餐呢，一起過去吧。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯，好。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "真是的……跑到哪里去了？\n啊，Thomas，有看到 Aroma 吗？我要拿上学期的资料给她。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 A"], "content": "没耶。对了，上一堂音乐课结束后她好像待在音乐教室喔，要不要去看看？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "好，谢谢！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_5", "音乐"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哇！吓我一跳……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊，对不起对不起～好好听喔……好久没听到妳唱歌了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "谢谢。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "来，给妳，上学期的一些补充资料还有讲座的简报。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "好，谢谢妳。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊，不過妳应该不需要吧……明明进度落后了快一年，一回来成绩马上又追上我跟 Daniel 了。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "没有啦……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "对了，刚刚那是什么歌啊？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……我也不知道，突然觉得很怀念就唱了……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "喔喔，还是记得很多东西的嘛，妳的记忆一定也很快就能恢复的！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "说起来……Aroma 原来会弹钢琴的吗？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……咦？我不知道……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "从来没听妳弹过耶，好厉害！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……谢谢。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "真是的……别一直愁眉苦脸的嘛。妳真的很厉害耶，成绩又好，歌声也美，还那么多才多艺……重点是还长得那么可爱，皮肤也那么好，太犯规了！快点想起来自己是多棒的人啊～我搔我搔～\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "啊哈哈……讨厌，好痒啦……\n谢谢妳……不过……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "嗯？怎么了？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不知道……总觉得班上的人不是很喜欢我……\n以前……有发生过什么事吗？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "啊啊～那个啊……别管那些人啦！因为妳真的太完美了，她们只是忌妒妳而已，没事的！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "走吧！ Iris 在等我们吃午餐呢，一起过去吧。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯，好。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}